  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Matches is a 1 to 4 player party game. Race, shoot, golf, jump, and compete with your friends across a series of frenetic rounds. Level up to unlock new characters and power up your abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/7e430be3e15cec9925e96746734fb3fe.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or online, competing across a series of wildly different mini games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/545e0c18b9f516fd054b2483be39f719.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your special ability wisely in each round to out-smart your opponents. Freeze time with Medusa and shoot your way to victory while your friends are stuck; or become incorporeal as WooOOoo The Ghost and slide through the level as if it wasn't there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/fe118cfe8cc30e8397f868c1f218a0f0.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters and power up your abilities you progress through the large upgrade tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/4f6681ca41d774cee6a4d8033042e8aa.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/314f0a73268fe86f0ec1d0fb529cec8a.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/314f0a73268fe86f0ec1d0fb529cec8a.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/314f0a73268fe86f0ec1d0fb529cec8a.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your best foot forward and win in style with a wide range of outfits.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Matches is a 1 to 4 player party game. Race, shoot, golf, jump, and compete with your friends across a series of frenetic rounds. Level up to unlock new characters and power up your abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/7e430be3e15cec9925e96746734fb3fe.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/6a7fbc9bb694b3ea2d7bf6af97623b9d.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or online, competing across a series of wildly different mini games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/545e0c18b9f516fd054b2483be39f719.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/57a4765bcc13dc81c11cc5456b889260.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your special ability wisely in each round to out-smart your opponents. Freeze time with Medusa and shoot your way to victory while your friends are stuck; or become incorporeal as WooOOoo The Ghost and slide through the level as if it wasn't there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/fe118cfe8cc30e8397f868c1f218a0f0.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.webm?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/b5f5e17ba8119c0158e679687fbe181d.mp4?t=1758539787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters and power up your abilities you progress through the large upgrade tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/4f6681ca41d774cee6a4d8033042e8aa.webp?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/941890/extras/314f0a73268fe86f0ec1d0fb529cec8a.poster.avif?t=1758539787\" width=600 height=180 ><source src